# Stranger Things 5 Landing Page

Step into Hawkins one final time. This project is a cinematic, Netflix-inspired landing page created to capture the suspense, mystery, and high-stakes atmosphere of *Stranger Things 5*. Built with modern HTML and CSS, it combines immersive visuals, responsive design, and engaging storytelling to deliver a captivating user experience.

## Highlights

* Fully responsive design optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
* Cinematic hero section with immersive background imagery
* Dynamic typography and content hierarchy for enhanced readability
* Netflix-inspired UI/UX design principles
* Strategic text overlays and visual storytelling elements
* Clean, maintainable, and scalable code structure

## 🛠️ Technologies

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Flexbox
* Responsive Web Design
* Modern UI/UX Principles

##  Project Goal

This project was developed to strengthen front-end development skills while exploring entertainment-focused web design. It demonstrates the ability to transform a popular media franchise into an engaging digital experience through thoughtful layout design, responsive techniques, and compelling visual presentation.

##  What I Learned

* Creating visually impactful landing pages
* Building responsive layouts across multiple screen sizes
* Improving typography and content readability
* Applying UI/UX principles to enhance user engagement
* Structuring clean and maintainable front-end code

*"Every ending has a beginning. Hawkins' final chapter starts here."*
